title: Please Give Me Energy
description: One day during my normal college life. A girl, insisting she’s a succubus, tries to have sex with me. But… she says I stole her powers, so now I have to gather energy if I want to live? Since that day, girls have started to become obsessed with me. “The smell you give off is driving me crazy… hurry, put it inside ♡”
author: UNO
